### NJE Event Platform — Backend Smoke Tests
### Run with VS Code REST Client extension
### Admin userId = 5 (promoted via SQL: UPDATE Users SET Role='Admin' WHERE Id=5)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminId = 5
@userId = 2

### ============================================================
### USERS
### ============================================================

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Teszt Felhasználó",
  "email": "teszt@nje.hu",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "institution": "NJE"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teszt@nje.hu",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### Get profile (auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### Short password — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "X",
  "email": "x@x.com",
  "password": "short"
}

###

### Duplicate email — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Duplicate",
  "email": "teszt@nje.hu",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### Update role (Admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/role
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

"Admin"

###

### Update role without auth — expect 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/role
Content-Type: application/json

"Admin"

###

### ============================================================
### EVENTS
### ============================================================

### Get all published events (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

###

### Get event by ID (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1

###

### Get non-existent event — expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/9999

###

### Create event (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "title": "NJE Konferencia 2026",
  "description": "Éves tudományos konferencia",
  "location": "GAMF Aula",
  "room": "A101",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-09-01T17:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 200,
  "isPublished": true
}

###

### Create event without title — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "x",
  "location": "x",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-09-01T17:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 10
}

###

### Create event with bad dates — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "title": "Bad Dates",
  "description": "x",
  "location": "x",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T17:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 10
}

###

### Create event without auth — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized",
  "description": "x",
  "location": "x",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-09-01T17:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 10
}

###

### Update event (Admin only) — replace 1 with actual event ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "title": "NJE Konferencia 2026 (frissítve)",
  "description": "Frissített leírás",
  "location": "GAMF Aula",
  "room": "B202",
  "startDate": "2026-09-01T09:00:00",
  "endDate": "2026-09-01T18:00:00",
  "maxParticipants": 250,
  "isPublished": true
}

###

### Get participants (Admin only) — replace 1 with actual event ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1/participants
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

###

### Get participants with User role — expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1/participants
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### Delete event (Admin only) — replace 1 with actual event ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

###

### ============================================================
### REGISTRATIONS
### ============================================================

### Join event (auth required) — replace eventId with actual ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/registrations/join
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Join event without auth — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/registrations/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Duplicate join — expect 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/registrations/join
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Check-in (Admin only) — replace qrData with actual QrToken from Users table
POST {{baseUrl}}/registrations/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "qrData": "REPLACE_WITH_USER_QR_TOKEN",
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Check-in with unknown QR — expect 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/registrations/checkin
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "qrData": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "eventId": 1
}

###

### Delete registration (Admin only) — replace 1 with actual registration ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/registrations/1
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

###

### Delete registration with User role — expect 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/registrations/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### ============================================================
### EVENT MODULES
### ============================================================

### Get modules for event (public) — replace 1 with actual event ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/1/modules

###

### Get modules for non-existent event — expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/9999/modules

###

### Create module (Admin only) — replace 1 with actual event ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/1/modules
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "moduleType": "InformationPage",
  "title": "Helyszín információ",
  "content": "GAMF Aula, 1. emelet, A szárny",
  "sortOrder": 1
}

###

### Create Map module
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/1/modules
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "moduleType": "Map",
  "title": "Térkép",
  "content": "https://maps.google.com/?q=Kecskemet+GAMF",
  "sortOrder": 2
}

###

### Update module (Admin only) — replace 1/1 with actual eventId/moduleId
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/1/modules/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "moduleType": "UsefulInformation",
  "title": "Hasznos információk",
  "content": "Parkolás ingyenes az intézmény udvarán.",
  "sortOrder": 3
}

###

### Delete module (Admin only) — replace 1/1 with actual eventId/moduleId
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/1/modules/1
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

###

### ============================================================
### NEWS
### ============================================================

### Get all news (public, ordered by CreatedAt desc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/news

###

### Get news by category (case-insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/news/category/General

###

### Get news by category uppercase
GET {{baseUrl}}/news/category/GENERAL

###

### Create news (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/news
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminId}}

{
  "title": "Fontos bejelentés",
  "content": "Az NJE konferencia regisztrációja megnyílt.",
  "category": "General"
}

###

### Create news without auth — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/news
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized",
  "content": "x",
  "category": "x"
}

###

### Create news with User role — expect 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/news
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "title": "Forbidden",
  "content": "x",
  "category": "x"
}
